ppy/osu-wiki.summary: Recent activities in the osu-wiki repository include updates to the MWC 7K 2025 team listing, addition of new tournament articles such as ANZT6W, and other contributions to the osu! wiki. ppy/osu.summary: The osu repository has seen significant activity, including a pull request to speed up the metronome in the timing screen when pressing the control key, and the addition of basic difficulty and performance calculation for the Autopilot mod on the osu! ruleset. Other contributions focus on improving the game's mechanics, such as osu!taiko rhythm considerations, demonstrating the community's ongoing efforts to enhance the gaming experience.

ppy/osu-web.summary: In the osu-web repository, a notable pull request aims to replace ts-loader and terser with swc, a tool for compiling TypeScript and optimizing JavaScript. This change seeks to improve the development process and performance of the osu web application, contributing to a more efficient and streamlined user experience.
